            with the most points wins!!
           </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button
    class='modal-close is-large'
    aria-label='close'
    aria-label='close'
    onclick="document.getElementById('modal3').style.display='none'"
  ></button>
</div>
